text.tspan: The product(s) or container(s) to which this tag is
attached is (are) controlled under authority of the
Agricultural Marketing Act and is (are) not to be
used, moved or altered in any manner without
the expressed permission of an authorized
reperentative of the United States Department of
Agriculture. The unauthorized removal or alteration
of this tag or utilization of the tagged product(s) is
a violation of the Agricultural Marketing Act of 1946,
as amended and regulations issued thereunder.
